title: 15 Minute Gentle BEGINNERS HIIT Workout | The Body Coach TV
description:
15 moves | 30 seconds work | 30 seconds rest

March on the spot
Side stars
Butt kick punches
Sumo squats
Knee smashes
Reverse lunge/step back arms to sky
Side lunges
Straight punches
Running man
Squat lateral kicks
Jog on the spot
Sumo squat pulse and stand
High plank
Lateral floor touches
Climb the rope

comments: I’m going to start on this journey. I can’t keep going down this unhealthy path. Thanks for posting when I was in a bad place. It’s a sign to start!
it’s so nice to see a video actually targeted towards beginners!! this felt achievable whilst still being rewarding
It's been a whole year since I last exercised and now I'm back!  Happy birthday, Joe!!!

Joe thank you! I have been trying to find motivation for months to get back in shape.  But this is the first workout I’ve actually enjoyed that also has felt like it’s actually doing something! Now I’ve finally worked out two days in a row, and I’m looking forward to doing it again tomorrow. Thank you!
Thank you Joe for keeping me motivated when I really can’t be bothered!
